@haileylangland faces off against @leannepelosi in the final battle of @naturalselection Round 1 DUELS 💥

📺 WATCH the PELOSI VS. LANGLAND DUELS and more now on Red Bull TV and find out which riders will move on to Stage_02 🔗 in bio and stories.

Mine and @leannepelosi @naturalselection Duel is out now. 

Getting to shadow @leannepelosi was such an amazing experience.  She is a guru of the mountains, a super talented snowboarder, and above all a new mom of 7 months! I was so inspired watching her ride on our duelsday, she is a true bad ass!

Thank you to Leanne and the awesome crew we had out there with us, as well as @naturalselection for putting on the event.

Watch the duel by going to the link in my bio. 😊

Hailey Langland’s season was one for the ages, as she stepped up in Revelstoke and took home third place and then immediately after the event, hopping in a heli to head out and session an untouched and unridden venue in prime conditions. Alongside 11 other riders, @haileylangland once again proved why she is one of the most promising backcountry riders of today’s generation.
